channel.title: [RS-2 Beta]Project Osiris 194
channel.description:
[img]http://img855.imageshack.us/img855/8278/rslogof.gif[/img]
[b]This thread is about recreating a RS-2 Beta. This is not an attempt to make a RS-2 Beta remake, this is only a project I'm working on for fun. There's alot of work to be done, so wish me good luck.[/b] [hr] I've quit xEpicz and the Subsonic project. I'm working on Osiris and RuneFocus atm.
I'll keep updating this.
Back in Development!
Updates:
[ul][li]Added level up messages [/li] [li]Adding skill experience [/li] [li]re-writing the action sender class [/li] [li]Finished leveling up [/li] [li]Started a herb cleaning system [/li] [li]Bones burying [/li] [li]Started Emotions [/li] [li][font=verdana][size=13px]The server now has interfaces (game interfaces, not java interfaces) and chat bar interfaces support.[/size][/font][font=verdana][size=13px] 15.9.2011[/size][/font][/li] [li][font=verdana][size=13px]Updated the level up method. It now sends the correct chatbox interfaces. And correct messages. 15.9.2011[/size][/font][/li] [li][font=verdana][size=13px]Created an item class, of which you can make item(id, amount) objects. Just like hyperion. 15.9.2011[/size][/font][/li] [li]Added a graphic system, working on all gfx's now[/li] [li]Finished Emotions (found the right ids)[/li] [li]Renamed some interface textures[/li] [li]A lovely welcome screen[/li] [li]Cleaning out the client class[/li] [li]Working dialogues[/li] [li]Searching for glitches[/li] [li]Started working on a Woodcutting system[/li] [li]Started working on a NPC system[/li][/ul]
[hr] Media:

[img]http://img717.imageshack.us/img717/7613/194fally.png[/img]

Leveling with interfaces [img]http://img571.imageshack.us/img571/3273/levelingup.png[/img]
